{"tid":563143,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺『意頭』呢樣野真係好on9","createTime":"2018-02-16T15:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T01:41:04.000Z","uid":40525,"like":25,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ee23b657047ae9e04a1a8e45aff6dc7d7ca3903e","tid":563143,"uid":40525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"屌，講左咁撚多年恭喜發財咪又係咁窮。<br />\n<br />\n啲廚師又係9下9下煮個飯都要食字<br />\n／／細輝經歷過剝牙後「牙痛到眼淚水都飆出來，食條菜都赤赤痛」，令他開始構思有甚麼菜式牙痛都能食，特別讓面對牙齒退化問題的長者能「重拾好味的感覺」。他曾經與牙醫朋友討論，最後設計出一系列無牙老虎宴的菜譜。無牙老虎宴的頭盤，材料中有魚，新年亦可拿個意頭，年年有餘，新春長者最希望兒孫滿堂，咕嚕玉用果酸代替醋酸調味／／<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2C1oZhX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2C1oZhX&d=O1CNgcZBuqpbfBX1NHLk1pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c8d7f46b\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2C1oZhX</a>"},{"pid":"2fc47249b2859e5f51c59c8b12c307b68e1e7ca1","tid":563143,"uid":157304,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通新年講咗個死字<br />\n你真係會死咩<br />\n祝鳩咗你幾十年恭喜發財<br />\n你都未發財啦死窮撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd17ed9f76af2d99de0f7e32e55c15e29e444fbe","tid":563143,"uid":45431,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:35:27.000Z","msg":"講幾句好聽說話聽完心情好啲又要俾你屌<br />\n定係你見親好友親朋都叫人死全家?"},{"pid":"e6eebd6be00ac9ef88d33e87b2a7940fdb10b9fc","tid":563143,"uid":22302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:36:28.000Z","msg":"髮菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82935c83ff4bf59f8109ed2f60a31dda4f00a49f","tid":563143,"uid":109050,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T15:50:38.000Z","msg":"從來都唔信呢D野,仲好反感"},{"pid":"b90082e090873595d2f507d848129cc9caa4e538","tid":563143,"uid":125079,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0